rgy (feminine element) of cosmos is of three types - one that causes object=
ification in consciousness, one that sustains objectification in consciousn=
ess and one that ends objectification in consciousness. These three aspects=
 are represented by Mahakali, Mahalakshmi and Mahasaraswati, the deities of=
 the 3 charitras of Saptashati or Chandipath or Devi Mahatmyam.
=A0
Various=
 higher beings emanate from these three basic types of higher kinetic energ=
y to aid in the respective high level processes. Please bear in mind that d=
ifferent male deities represents different types of potential energy of con=
sciousness, playing specific roles based on the combination of gunas, and d=
ifferent female deities represent different types of kinetic energy within =
consciousness, again playing specific roles based on the combination of gun=
as. It is all play of energies in the end.
