=A0
BTW, Nara=
yana or Purushottama is the absolute potential energy of cosmos. The initia=
l Mahalakshmi is the projection of that potential energy as kinetic energy.=
 Don't worry too much about the names. She is not the same as Mahalakshmi o=
f the 3 Mahadevis just because of the name. She could as well have been cal=
led Aadyaa Shakti or Naaraayani. To remove confusion, we may call her Aadya=
adi Mahalakshmi (in the terminology of Lakshmi Hridayam from "Atharva Rahas=
yam", which is one of my favorite prayers). Aadyaadi Mahalakshmi personifie=
s the entire kinetic energy of cosmos.
